import React from 'react'
import { Grid } from '@mui/material'

const AboutUs = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}>
          <Item>xs=4</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4}>
          <Item>xs=4</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={8}>
          <Item>xs=8</Item>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default AboutUs
